{"tid":787093,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"[日文][冷門band] Petrolz (東京事變吉他手)","createTime":"2018-08-20T11:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T04:31:03.000Z","uid":113250,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2227020b1f2b005f12dadf39c5861818404dea23","tid":787093,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:41:28.000Z","msg":"最近留意到隊band, 雖然都唔算新既, 叫 <strong>Petrolz</strong> ( ペトロールズ), 由東京事變既吉他手<strong>浮雲</strong>(正名: 長岡亮介) 圖左, 同三浦淳悟(Bass)圖中, 河村俊秀(Drum)圖右喺2005年創立, 主打indie rock同jazz (我都唔知歸納佢地做咩type好)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jnct3lmb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjnct3lmb&h=d2772618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比較特別嘅地方喺佢地主張大家聽live好過cd, 因為live嘅表現特別係bass, 所傳遞的情感係CD遠遠不及的。亦因為係咁佢地首張CD [仮免] 只有喺會場限定咁賣200張, 聽講上網個炒價好高, 有見過去到10k HKD左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n講番浮雲先, 令佢比較多人認識既歌/片可能係因為椎名林檎首&lt;長く短い祭&gt;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YLfkgo-3_sk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYLfkgo-3_sk&d=63RKd3urOAr6ZlDprLlRoGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=0deb8b2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YLfkgo-3_sk</a><br />\n<br />\n不過當東京事變解散左之後, 佢就行番自己輕鬆既style, 推介住幾首先:<br />\n<br />\n1. Profile<br />\n(林宥嘉cover為 - 新預感)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aYRGVa4K6JM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaYRGVa4K6JM&d=63RKd3urOAr6ZlDprLlRoGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=1bb19a77\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aYRGVa4K6JM</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 雨 (比較多人識呢首)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L7iPiD_6AEw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL7iPiD_6AEw&d=63RKd3urOAr6ZlDprLlRoGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=74cfdb12\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L7iPiD_6AEw</a><br />\n<br />\n同場加映佢喺椎名林檎百鬼夜行live到cover既舊歌 - 夢の途中<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/10WLu7FNswM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F10WLu7FNswM&d=63RKd3urOAr6ZlDprLlRoGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=bf2f2426\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/10WLu7FNswM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後講番CD, 暫時淨係喺Amazon見到有等賣, 其他網得ACC format download<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有買到或者聽過Petrolz?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4236c75de6b4b0a9c2821819b3cc6bedd6f234a8","tid":787093,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:42:36.000Z","msg":"我推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da32fd164c202046fb911c58424aba6d5f0cedce","tid":787093,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cb226bc17218982727a23cb6a48f175bf68cd0","tid":787093,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61b2a3c55c19074284b108eee9461878a92ee2e","tid":787093,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac2332f15e88259a4a2742d7cf6a9e92f235f7e","tid":787093,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:31:03.000Z","msg":"我有佢地三角形果隻碟"}]}